!! MIIT Beian Number

;Your MIIT ICP/Service Record Number: (for example, `ShangaiICPPreparate12345678No.-1` or `Seguridad de la red publica de Tianjin12345678901234No.`)
:<$edit-text tiddler="$:/plugins/linonetwo/beian-miit/configs/MIITBeianNumber" tabindex=-1 focus=false cancelPopups="yes" fileDrop=no tag="input" placeholder="Complete su numero de registro" />

''Note:'' When you fill in the beian number, it will be displayed at the bottom of the page with a link to https://beian.miit.gov.cn. Leave it empty to hide the beian footer.
